Package main.command

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddCommand
    Command class for Add operations.

    Command
    The base Command class.
    All commands should extend this class.
    Overwrite the isValidArguments(), isCommandAllowed() and executeAction() to implement the command's functionality.

    If you wish for the command to be executed on existing tasks, try extending TargetedCommand, which extends this class, instead.
    CommandController
    Handles the parsing of commands.

    SearchCommand
    Command class for Search operations.
    TargetedCommand
    Any command that "acts" on existing tasks should extend TargetedCommand.
    TargetedCommand gives the functionality to parse task numbers, absolute task Ids, and to act on tasks by specifying keywords.
    TaskIdSet
    A set of task IDs that is used for a command operation.
